HEADWORD: Altercate
<hw>Al"ter*cate</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp.
& p. p.</pos> <conjf>Altercated</conjf>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
